# Cross-platform line-ending policy.
# This repo is checked out on both Windows (local Claude Code) and Linux (cloud routine),
# so normalize text to LF in the repository and keep the working tree LF everywhere.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Exception: Windows batch files need CRLF — cmd.exe mis-parses LF-terminated lines.
*.bat text eol=crlf
*.cmd text eol=crlf
